high_descs: Turn around and cross the room to face the sink.
Pick up the knife in the sink.
Turn left and cross the room to face the kitchen table.
Cut the tomato on the table into slices.
Turn right and step forward to face the cabinet on the left end of the counter.
Place the knife in the cabinet on the left end of the counter.
Turn left and step forward to face the tomato on the kitchen table.
Pick up a slice of tomato on the kitchen table.
Turn around and cross the room to face the microwave.
Heat the tomato slice in the microwave and remove it.
Turn around and cross the room and turn right to face the fridge.
Place the tomato slice in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: To heat a tomato slice and place it in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the sink.
Pick up the gray knife in the left sink.
Turn right and go to the round gray table across the room.
Slice the red tomato on the table.
Turn right and go to the cabinet left of the stove.
Place the knife in the cabinet.
Turn around and go back to the round gray table.
Pick up one slice of tomato.
Turn around and go to the microwave across the kitchen on the other side.
Remove the tomato slice after heating it in the microwave.
Turn around and go to the front of the refrigerator across the kitchen.
Place the tomato slice ion the top shelf in the refrigerator.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated slice of tomato in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the sink on the opposite side.
Pick up the knife from the sink.
Turn around and walk to the black table on your right.
Cut the tomato on the table into slices.
Turn right and walk to the cabinet next to the fridge.
Open the cabinet door and put the knife in the cabinet. Close the door.
Turn around and head to the tomato on the table.
Pick up one slice of tomato.
Turn right and walk across the kitchen to reach the microwave at the end.
Open the microwave door, put the tomato slice in the microwave. Close the door and cook for 5 minutes. Open the door, take out the tomato slice and close the door.
Turn around and go to the fridge on your right. Open the fridge door.
Put the potato slice in the fridge and close the fridge door.
anns.task_desc: Cook a tomato slice in a microwave and put the tomato slice in a fridge.
